sources.description:
CLASSIC MOVIE MONDAY
Stars: John Carroll, Movita, Polly Ann Young
Writer: Jack London (story by)
Director: George Waggner

In this rarely-seen JACK LONDON adaptation, a spoiled New York City socialite and his dog sidekick are sent to a Canadian Radium Mine to leave behind his raucous lifestyle.
